| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-1000 — Recovery Inhibition (clop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e2e6eaa0-58f3-5b9b-86e1-a7cf157334ed"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
